_Pi’el_ Imperative for regular shorushim:
The [[{{_pi’el_ imperative}} form]] follows the following conjugations for [[regular shorushim]]:
|            | *Masculine* | *Feminine* |
| *Singular* | זַמֵּן <br> _zamein!_ <br> [to a man] invite! | זַמְּנִי <br> _zamni!_ <br> [to a woman] invite! |
| *Plural*   | זַמְּנוּ <br> _zamnu!_ <br> [to men] invite! | זַמֵּנָּה <br> _zameinnau!_ <br> [to women] invite! |
For any regular shoresh, you can replace the letters ‎ז, ‎מ, and ן above with the letters of your shoresh to produce the proper conjugations.
